study_description: The marine metagenome Third Party Annotation (TPA) assembly was derived from the primary whole genome shotgun (WGS) data set: PRJNA330363.  This project includes samples from the following biomes: Environmental, Aquatic, Marine.
study_title: EMG produced TPA metagenomics assembly of the Marine microbial communities from expanding oxygen minimum zones in Line P, North Pacific Ocean - fosmids plate 1 metagenome (marine metagenome) data set.
